---
// Services component with feature grid
---

<section class="bg-gray-100">
  <div class="py-16 xl:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 xl:px-16">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-black mb-3">
          Is Your Panel Ready for Today's Demands?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Many Las Vegas homes have outdated systems. With high-efficiency ACs,
          home offices, and EV chargers, old panels are pushed to their limits.
          It might be time for an upgrade if you're experiencing:
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16">
        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-3 md:row-start-1 md:row-end-2"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-black text-white/85 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-accent self-center translate-y-[-2px]"
              ></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent">
                Frequently Tripping Breakers
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              A clear sign your panel is overloaded and can't handle your home's
              electrical demand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-start-1 md:col-end-2 md:row-start-1 md:row-end-2"
        >
          <div
            class="border border-gray-300 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-black self-center translate-y-[-2px]"
              ></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">
                Flickering or Dimming Lights
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Especially when a large appliance like an AC unit kicks on.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-start-3 md:col-end-4 md:row-start-1 md:row-end-2"
        >
          <div
            class="border border-gray-300 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-black self-center translate-y-[-2px]"
              ></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">
                Buzzing or Crackling Sounds
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              A dangerous sign of loose wiring or a failing breaker that
              requires immediate attention.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-start-1 md:col-end-2 md:row-start-2 md:row-end-3"
        >
          <div
            class="border border-gray-300 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-black self-center translate-y-[-2px]"
              ></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">
                Burning Smell or Scorch Marks
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              If you notice this, call a licensed electrician immediately as
              it's a fire hazard.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-3 md:row-start-2 md:row-end-3"
        >
          <div
            class="border border-gray-300 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-black self-center translate-y-[-2px]"
              ></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">An Old Fuse Box</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We operate with full licensing and insurance to do every jobFuse
              boxes are obsolete and lack the modern safety features of a
              circuit breaker panel.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-start-3 md:col-end-4 md:row-start-2 md:row-end-3"
        >
          <div
            class="border border-gray-300 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-black self-center translate-y-[-2px]"
              ></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Adding Major Appliances</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Planning for an EV charger, hot tub, or major renovation often
              requires more power.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
